summary: An Ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2709 for the improvement of Whitman Avenue from Kilbourne Street to North Forty-fifth Street, and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues; all in the City of Seattle, by re-surfacing, curbs and gutters, concrete sidewalks, wooden crosswalks, and providing for the necessary surface drainage, under Ordinance No. 31833, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
